und in the spatial patterns of the surface current as measured by high-frequency (HF) radars. Preliminary results concerning the ROMS forecast skill and predictability are also presented. Future plans to improve the ROMS forecast system with a particular focus on assimilation of HF radar current measurements are discussed. ?? 2008 Elsevier Ltd.},
author = {Chao, Yi and Li, Zhijin and Farrara, John and McWilliams, James C. and Bellingham, James and Capet, Xavier and Chavez, Francisco and Choi, Jei Kook and Davis, Russ and Doyle, Jim and Fratantoni, David M. and Li, Peggy and Marchesiello, Patrick and Moline, Mark A. and Paduan, Jeff and Ramp, Steve},
